wikipedia_page.main: Michael Sydney Foster (born 3 February 1939) is an English former footballer who played as a winger in the Football League for Colchester United and Millwall. He was also signed to Leicester City and Norwich City, though he made no appearances for those clubs.

response: Michael or Mike Foster may refer to:

* Mike Foster, American activist, co-founder of XXXchurch.com
